&lt;Bower industries Inc> saidit changed its name to Metalclad Corp and has restructured aloan agreement with its bank.    Under the pact, a 3.5-mln-dlr revolving credit line will beconverted to a 1.8-mln-dlr six year note and a 1.7-mln-dlrrevolving line of credit.    The company said it is also restructuring a 4,011,000-dlrdebt to another creditor, whereby two mln dlrs will beforgiven, 1,950,000 dlrs will be converted into two long-termnotes due April, 1989 and 61,000 dlrs has been included in aline of credit. Reuter&#3;